    {
      "scene_index": 2,
      "label": "第二场",
      "characters_present": [
        "秦王",
        "赵艳容",
        "赵高"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（秦王上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦王",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孤王御驾到龙庭，文臣武将朝寡人。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵高上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵高",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "启奏万岁：小女昨晚得了疯病！"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "昨晚灯光之下还好，即日怎么得了疯？"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵高",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "天有不测风云，人有旦夕祸福。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孤王赐她龙车凤辇带上金殿。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵高",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "领旨。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵高下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "传御林军走上。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四卒同上。赵艳容、赵高同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵艳容",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "午门外下了那龙车凤辇，"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵艳容",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "行一步来至在御驾跟前。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵艳容",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "看昏王他把我怎样旨传。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵艳容",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "到于今顾不得抛头露面"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵高",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿呀，上面就是万岁。上前参见。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵艳容",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我晓得呦！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵艳容",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "上面敢是皇帝老官？恭喜你万福，贺喜你发财！"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "见了寡人为何不跪？"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵艳容",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你大人不下跪，罗喏喏我生员是不跪的！"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "原来是个疯癫女子。寡人好笑呵！哈哈哈……"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵艳容",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你好笑，我也好笑！哈哈哈……"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "寡人笑你疯癫，你笑寡人何来？"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵艳容",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你笑我疯癫，我就笑无道的昏君！"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "寡人有道，怎说无道？"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵艳容",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦，你要问你的无道，列位大人老哥了，你也听了：只因老王在世，东修岱海，"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵艳容",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "西建阿房，南修五岭，北造万里长城。直指望江山万代，谁想你这昏君贪淫"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵艳容",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "恋酒，不理朝事。我想这天下乃人人之天下，并非你一人之天下，我看你这江"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵艳容",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "山未必能长久了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵艳容",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "想此事气得我乌云扯乱，"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵艳容",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "气得我舌尖儿咬破牙关！"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "殿前武士，刀门架起！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵艳容",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "住了！我乃丞相之女，指挥老爷之妻，你们放肆大胆，还不与我退下！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵艳容",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "我手中有镔铁定要试斩，"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵艳容",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "将这班众狂徒立斩马前！"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "再若提起疯癫，抓头来见！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵高",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿吓，再若提起疯癫，万岁就要杀头了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵艳容",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "住了，动不动你就要杀头！我且问你，一个人头割将下来，难道还长得上么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵高",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "长不上了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵艳容",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓呵，吓呵，爷爷，我的儿吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵高",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呸！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵艳容",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "我这里忙下金銮，"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵艳容",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "那昏王怎知我袖内机关？"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵艳容",
          "line_type": "笑",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哈哈哈……"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵艳容下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵高",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老臣领罪。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "罚俸三月，退班！"
        }
      ],
